name: Differential access - limited
description__value: Objects or media are only viewable by authenticated users but not downloadable; objects/media are only downloadable by admin users.

name: Differential access - open
description__value: Objects or media are viewable by anonymous users but not downloadable. Objects/media are only downloadable by admin users.

name: Limited access
description__value: Objects can only be viewed and downloaded by authenticated users, metadata isn't searchable by anonymous users. Anonymous users don't see the node and can't find it through search.

name: Open access
description__value: Objects can be viewed and downloaded by anonymous users.
